text: Kansas City Confidential is a 1952 American crime drama movie directed by Phil Karlson and starring John Payne, Coleen Gray, Preston Foster, Neville Brand, Lee Van Cleef, Jack Elam, Dona Drake, Carleton Young. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1952 crime drama movies Category:American crime drama movies Category:Movies directed by Phil Karlson
